The paper discusses optimization methods for machine learning, specifically for maximizing the Area Under Receiver Operating Characteristic Curve (AUC), which is commonly used in classification tasks. This falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and systems and control (cs.SY). However, since the focus is on optimization, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely categories, followed by cs.CV, cs.NE, and cs.SY.
